# Leap Year

year = eval(input("Enter a year: "))

# Check if the year is a leap year. Displays true or false in output
isLeapYear = (year % 4 == 0 and year % 100 != 0) or \
    (year % 400 == 0)

# Display the output
print("Is", year, "a leap year?", isLeapYear)

'''
RESULTS:

Enter a year: 2010
Is 2010 a leap year? False
Press any key to continue . . .


Enter a year: 2008
Is 2008 a leap year? True
Press any key to continue . . .
'''
